'''Venture into the (Un)known''' is a multi-world [[wikipedia:Alternate_reality_game|ARG]] experience, with the goal of finding [[VRRat]]. This event was community made and promoted by VRChat from March 16 to March 30, 2026.<ref>[https://x.com/VRChat/status/2033635390498685100 VRRat has gone missing! Please help us find him...] on ''X''. Retrieved March 31, 2026.</ref> While the event has "ended", the worlds to the event are still accessible.

